    "description": "<strong>Way Of Vulcan</strong> <br>is a medieval fantasy game about mining and blacksmithing, where war rages between nations.<br>Our character and his brother work for a blacksmith. when the war draws near to the kingdom, our brother is needed for the army and it is up to us to carry out his duties.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/7b68638f550a58ae7a0e7943c1ce0be3.avif?t=1669400250\" width=608 height=160 /></span><br> <br><strong>Mining</strong><br>Collect required gems in multiple huge caves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/f8a06da19be26b1f6f8c7c293efd08f9.poster.avif?t=1669400250\" width=508 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/f8a06da19be26b1f6f8c7c293efd08f9.webm?t=1669400250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/f8a06da19be26b1f6f8c7c293efd08f9.mp4?t=1669400250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gather the additional materials</strong><br>The equipments you will make is not only with gems, but you also need special materials and there are different ways to collect these materials.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/eb1f35474ae6692e6846e12b58682540.poster.avif?t=1669400250\" width=508 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/eb1f35474ae6692e6846e12b58682540.webm?t=1669400250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/eb1f35474ae6692e6846e12b58682540.mp4?t=1669400250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Crafting</strong><br>Produce the materials needed for the equipments and have our master to make it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/70e976964ca936d8994e7debeecd48de.poster.avif?t=1669400250\" width=508 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/70e976964ca936d8994e7debeecd48de.webm?t=1669400250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/70e976964ca936d8994e7debeecd48de.mp4?t=1669400250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Quests</strong><br>Take quests from people and complete them all and for each completed quest you unlock the weapons you crafted in your museum.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/fb0728a14dd1f9b340dab8aa0d9d2699.poster.avif?t=1669400250\" width=508 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/fb0728a14dd1f9b340dab8aa0d9d2699.webm?t=1669400250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146270/extras/fb0728a14dd1f9b340dab8aa0d9d2699.mp4?t=1669400250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Museum</strong><br>You can see every equipment you made in here.",
